      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "SFn_PromptPreview"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "[ Prompt ]\nA breathtaking, highly detailed, and hyper-realistic landscape photograph suitable for a Windows desktop wallpaper. The scene is a deep night sky filled with the Milky Way galaxy, rendered in stunning, vibrant colors (nebula tones of magenta, cyan, and electric blue). Foreground elements include silhouetted mountain peaks or jagged rocks covered lightly in snow, providing a strong contrast to the brilliant sky. The foreground should incorporate some subtle atmospheric details like wispy clouds catching starlight, enhancing depth. Use cinematic lighting, deep contrast, and an extremely wide-angle shot (ultra-wide lens perspective). High resolution, 16:9 aspect ratio, dramatic, awe-inspiring, award-winning astrophotography style. --ar 16:9\n\n──────────────────────\n[ Negative Prompt ]\nblurry, low quality, amateur photography, saturated colors only, artificial glow, text, watermark, cartoonish, noisy.\n\n──────────────────────\n[ Raw LLM Output ]\n{\n\"prompt\": \"PROMPT: A breathtaking, highly detailed, and hyper-realistic landscape photograph suitable for a Windows desktop wallpaper. The scene is a deep night sky filled with the Milky Way galaxy, rendered in stunning, vibrant colors (nebula tones of magenta, cyan, and electric blue). Foreground elements include silhouetted mountain peaks or jagged rocks covered lightly in snow, providing a strong contrast to the brilliant sky. The foreground should incorporate some subtle atmospheric details like wispy clouds catching starlight, enhancing depth. Use cinematic lighting, deep contrast, and an extremely wide-angle shot (ultra-wide lens perspective). High resolution, 16:9 aspect ratio, dramatic, awe-inspiring, award-winning astrophotography style. --ar 16:9\"\n,\n\"negative_prompt\": \"blurry, low quality, amateur photography, saturated colors only, artificial glow, text, watermark, cartoonish, noisy.\"\n}"
      ]
